OL,7,FA dangerous driver killed one person
OL,8,Fand seriously injured three others in
OL,9,Fa crash when he sped along a country
OL,10,Froad at 85mph to get home for his
OL,11,FSunday dinner.
OL,13,FOne motorist who saw farm labourer
OL,14,FOwen Rutherford tear along the A68 in
OL,15,FNorthumberland in his Seat Leon had
OL,16,Fcommented "he's going to kill someone"
OL,17,Fjust moments before the the fatal
OL,18,Fcollision with David Hain's vehicle.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/15
