OL,5,Cdinner'
OL,7,FNewcastle Crown Court heard Mr Hain,
OL,8,F69, died as a result of multiple
OL,9,Finjuries, his wife Philippa Hain
OL,10,Fsuffered broken ribs and facial
OL,11,Ffractures, their daughter Megan, 25,
OL,12,Fsuffered serious brain damage from
OL,13,Fwhich she will never recover and their
OL,14,Ffamily dog Millie was killed.
OL,16,FAnother victim, who was their
OL,17,Fpassenger, suffered a broken neck.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/15
