OL,7,FOn Monday (24 February), Judge Edward
OL,8,FBindloss jailed Rutherford, who had a
OL,9,Fbreakdown product of cocaine in his
OL,10,Fsystem at the time of the crash, for
OL,11,F11 years and four months with a 19-
OL,12,Fyear driving ban.
OL,14,FThe judge told Rutherford: "You were
OL,15,Fin a rush, you said to the probation
OL,16,Fofficer, to go for Sunday lunch.
OL,18,F"In the pre-sentence report you also
OL,19,Facknowledge you took unnecessary
OL,20,Frisks."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/15
