OL,7,FJudge Bindloss added: "No sentence I
OL,8,Fpass will bring David back nor undo
OL,9,Fwhat has been done.
OL,11,F"All I can do is try to pass a
OL,12,Fsentence that recognises the high
OL,13,Fculpability of this dangerous driving
OL,14,Fand the extensive harm inflicted so
OL,15,Fneedlessly on a family."
