OL,7,FProsecutor Nick Dry told the court the
OL,8,FHains, with four generations of the
OL,9,Fextended family, had travelled to
OL,10,FNorthumberland for what should have
OL,11,Fbeen a "joyous" celebration of a
OL,12,Frelative's 60th birthday.
OL,14,FLoved ones from Wales and Scotland had
OL,15,Ftravelled to the event.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/15
