OL,7,FOn the morning of 1 October 2023, the
OL,8,Fgroup had enjoyed bacon sandwiches at
OL,9,Fthe barn conversion where they were
OL,10,Fall staying before a group, travelling
OL,11,Fin two cars, headed to Kielder Forrest
OL,12,Ffor a walk.
OL,14,FIt was during the journey to Kielder
OL,15,Fthat Mr Hain's vehicle was hit as he
OL,16,Fturned onto the A68 at Beukley Bank,
OL,17,Fon a blind summit.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/15
