OL,7,FThe court heard Richardson, who had
OL,8,Fovertaken several cars on the stretch
OL,9,Fof road, smashed into the driver's
OL,10,Fside of Mr Hain's vehicle, which was
OL,11,Fshunted off the carriageway and onto a
OL,12,Fgrass verge.
OL,14,FRelatives from the car in front rushed
OL,15,Fto help the injured and contacted
OL,16,Fother family members, who arrived and
OL,17,Fgave what assistance they could while
OL,18,Fthey waited for the air ambulance.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/15
