OL,7,FMr Hain, whose seatbelt sheared off
OL,8,Fthrough the force of the impact, was
OL,9,Fthrown from his vehicle and suffered
OL,10,Fmultiple fractures and injuries to his
OL,11,Finternal organs. He died in hospital
OL,12,Ftwo days later.
OL,14,FPhilippa Hain spent 12 days in
OL,15,Fhospital with painful injuries,
OL,16,Fgrieving the loss of her husband of 27
OL,17,Fyears and fearing she may also lose
OL,18,Fher daughter.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/15
