OL,7,FMrs Hain, who lived with her husband
OL,8,Fin Wales, but has since moved to be
OL,9,Fwith their daughter in England, said
OL,10,Fin an impact statement: "On October 1
OL,11,F2023 my life and the lives of my
OL,12,Ffamily changed in terrible ways.
OL,14,F"The crash resulted in everyone who
OL,15,Fwas in the car being seriously injured
OL,16,Fand our beloved family dog Millie
OL,17,Fdying instantly on impact.
OL,19,F"Following the crash, I was badly
OL,20,Finjured and suffered from broken ribs
OL,21,Fand broken bones in my face.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/15
