OL,7,FMrs Hain said Megan was a "vibrant,
OL,8,Fbright 25-year-old" with her whole
OL,9,Ffuture ahead of her but added: "This
OL,10,Fhas all been taken away."
OL,12,FThe court heard Megan now lives in a
OL,13,Fcare home where all of her needs are
OL,14,Flooked after. She cannot respond,
OL,15,Fphysically or verbally but her mum
OL,16,Fsaid she is a "fighter" and there is
OL,17,Fhope she may in future be able to
OL,18,Fregain some elements of her life.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G13/15
