OL,7,FRutherford, who suffered minor
OL,8,Finjuries, told police at the scene he
OL,9,Fhad been "driving home for his dinner".
OL,11,FThe court heard he had been travelling
OL,12,Fat "no less than 85mph" at the time of
OL,13,Fthe collision and the anti lock
OL,14,Fbreaking system in his car was not
OL,15,Fworking at the time.
OL,17,FRutherford, 25, of Ridsdale,
OL,18,FNorthumberland, admitted causing death
OL,19,Fby dangerous driving and three of
OL,20,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,21,Fdriving.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G14/15
