OL,7,FHe was convicted of drink driving in
OL,8,FSeptember last year, while under
OL,9,Finvestigation for the fatal crash.
OL,11,FBrian Hegarty, defending, said
OL,12,FRutherford had a difficult upbringing,
OL,13,Fhas struggled to come to terms with
OL,14,Fwhat he did and understands the
OL,15,Fdevastation he caused.
